    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "We thought it would be even more cruel to have cut/copy/paste _not_ use x/c/v, since those are probably the most widely used shortcuts in the world.  But it's true that we could consider introducing a second prefix... We are going to run out of `C-m` options pretty soon, so perhaps a second group of keybindings would be a good idea.  Worth thinking about and planning for the long term; @ellisonbg, what's your take on this?\n"
  },
